last_episode_to_air.overview: After the events of Mexico, the Lynx regroup at a revived Lodge and prepare for an important coronation. Liz goes for a swim. Connie has a secret.

name: Lodge 49
overview: Dud is a deadbeat but charming ex-surfer who joins a fraternal order hoping to reclaim the simple, happy lifestyle he lost when his father died. Through the Lodge and his newfound connection with the other members, Dud will come to find the missing sense of purpose in his life and confront his deepest fears and greatest hopes.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: Dud's beloved fraternal order — the Ancient and Benevolent Order of the Lynx — is suffering under new rule by an ill-suited leader. Despite his mentor Ernie's lost faith, and his twin sister Liz's struggle with their past, Dud believes he is the key to restoring the Lodge to its former grandeur and putting the rightful king on the throne.

episodes.name: As Above, So Below
episodes.overview: Dud is deposited by fate at the doorstep of Lodge 49, a fraternal order which offers cheap beer and strange alchemical philosophies.

episodes.name: Moments of Truth in Service
episodes.overview: Dud becomes acquainted with the Lodge. Ernie battles with his fellow Lynx.

episodes.name: Corpus
episodes.overview: Liz and Dud hold a memorial for their father. Ernie and Connie spend the weekend together.

episodes.name: Sunday
episodes.overview: Dud and Ernie venture out on a mission in the kingdom of Long Beach. Liz spends her day off at work.

episodes.name: Paradise
episodes.overview: Dud's new relationship goes well. Ernie prepares for the Sovereign Protector ceremony.

episodes.name: The Mysteries
episodes.overview: Larry divulges the secrets of the Lodge to Ernie, while Dud makes an unusual discovery.

episodes.name: The Solemn Duty of the Squire
episodes.overview: A new visitor arrives at the Lodge with some troubling news.

episodes.name: Something from Nothing
episodes.overview: Dud and Ernie accompany Captain on a journey into the night. Liz attempts to climb the corporate ladder.

episodes.name: Apogee
episodes.overview: Band Night at the Lodge. Dud and Ernie are eager to close a deal with Captain, but all may not be what it seems.

episodes.name: Full Fathom Five
episodes.overview: The Lodge's fate hangs in limbo. Dud resigns himself to a new path. Liz reaches her breaking point.

episodes.name: All Circles Vanish
episodes.overview: The pool shop is under new ownership. Dud recuperates from his shark attack while searching for Ernie. Ernie deals with the aftermath of his adventure with El Confidente. Liz enters the TempJoy workforce.

episodes.name: The Slide
episodes.overview: Dud makes an enemy cleaning pools. Liz tries to hit bottom. A game of golf jeopardizes Ernie's career.

episodes.name: DisOrientation
episodes.overview: Ernie recounts his trip to Mexico and Dud sees a solution to all the Lodge's problems. Liz works at Higher Steaks. Dud and Liz spend time with a woman from their father's past.

episodes.name: Conjunctio
episodes.overview: Dud, Blaise and El Confidente fundraise for their upcoming adventure.

episodes.name: Estrella y Mar
episodes.overview: Liz goes into business with Lenore. Ernie reunites with Connie. Dud and Beth try out marriage. Blaise and Scott's conflict comes to a head.

episodes.name: Circles
episodes.overview: As the Lynx prepare for The Mystic Chords of Memory, Dud's wound worsens. Blaise glimpses the past. Liz goes on a journey at Orbis.

episodes.name: Exile
episodes.overview: Dud resumes his apprenticeship with Blaise. Ernie sees someone from his past. Ernie hits bottom. Liz goes to the mat for her employees.

episodes.name: Zugzwang
episodes.overview: L. Marvin Metz comes to the Lodge with Dud and Ernie. Liz gets a promotion and Scott goes for a walk.

episodes.name: Le Reve Impossible
episodes.overview: In a foreign land, the Lynx search for the Grail and Ernie embraces his fate. Janet pulls Liz into a scheme. Blammo.

episodes.overview: After the events of Mexico, the Lynx regroup at a revived Lodge and prepare for an important coronation. Liz goes for a swim. Connie has a secret.
